metadata.name: The King is Dead
metadata.description: It's May 2023. For moments I felt like a king in the web3 space, counted my time in here by number of successes. The last few months have been brutal, with lots of punches to the face that I had to take. The King is finally dead. Or, is it? Am I going to let these setbacks define me, or I am going to stand up again and fight for what I believe?
